  "body": "When we're too close to head, sometimes I see initial sync suspended because out-of-sync peers returns no block\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n```\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [SYNC]             info: Fetching blocks for 206809...206872 slot range\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [SYNC]          verbose: updating block target 206872\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [NETWORK]       verbose: sending beacon_blocks_by_range request to 16Uiu2HAmEFNUhawqweErEFPmMKhN5dnQkypT38nT6CT8Us6jkvUf requestId=6632994e9675f2ca, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [NETWORK]       verbose: sending beacon_blocks_by_range request to 16Uiu2HAmV2BjFPcY4QYRuWE5DxpS2KpfLogiSmVKe9Lp9mTt3XBU requestId=af03c0ced39b8b70, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [NETWORK]       verbose: receive beacon_blocks_by_range response with 0 chunks from 16Uiu2HAmV2BjFPcY4QYRuWE5DxpS2KpfLogiSmVKe9Lp9mTt3XBU requestId=af03c0ced39b8b70, encoding=ssz_snappy, body={\"startSlot\":206842,\"step\":1,\"count\":31}\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [NETWORK]       verbose: receive beacon_blocks_by_range response with 0 chunks from 16Uiu2HAmEFNUhawqweErEFPmMKhN5dnQkypT38nT6CT8Us6jkvUf requestId=6632994e9675f2ca, encoding=ssz_snappy, body={\"startSlot\":206809,\"step\":1,\"count\":33}\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [SYNC]             info: Imported blocks for slots:\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [SYNC]          verbose: last processed slot=null\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [SYNC]             warn: Didn't receive any valid block in given range\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [SYNC]             info: Fetching blocks for 206873...206936 slot range\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [SYNC]          verbose: updating block target 206936\r\n2020-07-28 11:39:04  [NETWORK]       verbose: sending beacon_blocks_by_range request to 16Uiu2HAmEFNUhawqweErEFPmMKhN5dnQkypT38nT6CT8Us6jkvUf requestId=3baf1675e08571be, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n```\r\n\r\nNote that I receive a lot of `Didn't receive any valid block in given range` warning. After a while it's suspended.",
